      <title>肯尼亚在税收抗议后努力稳定公共财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/kenya-struggles-to-stabilize-public-finances-after-tax-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚财政部长约翰·姆巴迪 (John Mbadi) 表示，由于财政部难以稳定紧张的公共财政，肯尼亚本财年刚开始两个月，预算缺口就扩大了 28%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/kenya-struggles-to-stabilize-public-finances-after-tax-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:33:02 GMT</pubDate>
