      <title>菲律宾参议院调查前市长银行账户资金流动情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/philippine-senate-probes-fund-flows-in-ex-mayor-s-bank-accounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因涉嫌洗钱而被免职的菲律宾市长周一在参议院面临质询，质询内容涉及进入其银行账户的数十亿比索，以及这些资金与一个以中国为中心的在线赌博中心有何关联。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/philippine-senate-probes-fund-flows-in-ex-mayor-s-bank-accounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
